      "title": "<span id=\"#18298\" class=\"scroll-m-16 text-3xl font-bold flex items-center\"><h1 class=\"inline !mb-1 scroll-m-16 text-3xl font-bold\">contrive</h1><div class=\"pl-2 flex-1 text-textSecondary text-xl font-serif\">(v.)</div></span>",
      "html": "<p>14世纪初， <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">controve, contreve</span>，“发明，设计”； 14世纪晚期，“通过计划或方案管理”，来自古法语 <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">controver</span>（现代法语 <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">controuver</span>）“发现，设计，想象”，源自晚期拉丁语 <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">contropare</span> “比较”（通过比喻），来自拉丁语 <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">com</span> “一起，共同”（见 <a href=\"/cn/word/con-\" title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of con- \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\">con-</a>) + <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">tropus</span> “歌曲，音乐模式”，源自希腊语 <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">tropos</span> “修辞格”（源自 PIE 词根 <a href=\"/cn/word/*trep-\" title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of *trep- \" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"crossreference notranslate\">*trep-</a> “转动”）。</p><ins class=\"adsbygoogle relative inline-block transition-all inline-block h-[250px] w-[300px]\" data-ad-slot=\"4000736339\" data-adtest=\"off\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"></ins><p>意义演变（在法语中）是从“巧妙地发明”到“虚假发明”。英语拼写方式的改变是由于15世纪同样未经解释的语音变化，也影响了 <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of briar \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/briar\">briar</a>， <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of friar \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/friar\">friar</a>， <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of choir \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/choir\">choir</a>。相关： <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">Contrived</i>； <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">contriving</i>。</p>"
    }
  ],
